strings: <voice_0x010016CD><se_def>China: It failed! A long time ago].
<voice_0x010016CE><se_def>China: As always, I met new people.
<voice_0x010016CF><se_def>China: You know that I am a very busy person. This is why I didn't like all the results at first. But it's good to see the old team again.
<voice_0x010016D0><se_def>China: But are you truly happy in the relationship? It doesn't have to be negative! if you find it difficult
<voice_0x010016D1><se_def>China: Do what you gotta do, my friend. When I leave the monastery.

<voice_0x010016D2><se_high>*: Angelo's so wonderful!
You know, he looks after children who don't have anywhere else to go, don't you?<page>*: He says he wants to repay all the kindness Abbot Francisco showed him when he was all alone in the world. Isn't he just the sweetest man you ever met!?
<voice_0x010016D5><se_def>China: You're greedy, don't tell others! Should have left the picture...
<voice_0x010016D6><se_def>China: See you soon <hero> Go outside and rest. Come to me when you are ready
<voice_0x010016D2><se_high>*: Wonderful angel! You know she takes care of the kids who don't know where to go, right?
<voice_0x010016D3>*: He wanted to thank Dean Francis for being so kind to him when he was alone.
<voice_0x010016D4>*: Isn't he the most handsome guy you've ever met?
<voice_0x010016D5><se_def>China: You're greedy, don't tell others! Should have left the picture...
